  "body": "üßê Motivation\r\nAs a role admin i want to suspend users to perform their role activities instead of revoking their roles for a specific time.\r\n\r\nüìù Details\r\n\r\n- A method which a `ROLE ADMIN` can call with `UNDERLYING ROLE` , `MALICIOUS USER ADDRESS` and a `TIMESTAMP` to set a time upto which that particular account is suspended to perform its activities.\r\n- A method which return a boolean to check whether the account is suspended or not (call this in hasRole function also).\r\n- A method to return the time remaining for ending of a suspension.",
